title: Anishinaabe (North American Indigenous peoples)

description: Preferred topical term to supplement or replace Library of Congress subject headings (LCSH) listed under "Close match." This term is acceptable for describing the Odawa, per an email from a representative of the Little River Band of Ottawa Indians, 2021-07-06. This term also is acceptable for describing the Odawa, Ojibwe, and Bodwéwadmik peoples more broadly, per an email from a representative of the Grand Traverse Band of Ottawa and Chippewa Indians, 2021-09-17.
